These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, chef, architect, social-worker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, thriller, scientific, zombie
4 different pets are kept: fish, snake, hedgehog, hamster
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, tennis, baseball, soccer
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, scooter, bus, subway
 1. the bartender is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the person watching zombie movies is the person watching zombie movies##1
 6. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 8. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 9. the architect is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
10. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
11. the bartender is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
12. the owner of the hedgehog is between the person watching scientific movies and the owner of the snake##2
13. the architect is the person driving the subway##1
14. the person driving the bus is the chef##1
15. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the chef##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |     4      |
| Job           | bartender | architect | social-worker  | chef    |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller     | zombie   | scientific  | drama  |
| Pet           | snake        | hedgehog    | hamster        | fish |
| Sport         | soccer    | tennis      | climbing   | baseball    |
| Transport     | tram  | subway     | scooter | bus |

