.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, lemonade, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, chess, puzzles, dancing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, romance, fantasy, epic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, classical, r&b, indie
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, volleyball, biathlon, handball
 1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 3. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
 4. the fan of indie is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 5. the person watching epic movies is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left##1
 7. the person drinking water is in an even position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
 9. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
10. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person who's sport is handball##1
11. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
12. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
13. the fan of classical is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | lemonade        | water       | 7up    | mirinda       |
| Hobby         | puzzles | chess      | dancing | fishing |
| Movie-Genre   | epic     | fantasy | romance  | disaster   |
| Music-Genre   | classical   | indie         | ambient   | r&b      |
| Sport         | volleyball      | weightlifting     | biathlon    | handball      |

