.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: lemon, pumpkin, cauliflower, grapefruit
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, analyst, social-worker, photographer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, reggae, classical, dubstep
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, biathlon, handball, snowboarding
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, jet-ski, van, tram
 1. the person who's sport is biathlon is the fan of reggae##1
 2. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 3. the person driving the tram is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the scientist##3
 5. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person eating pumpkin##3
 6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
 7. the photographer is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
 8. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 9. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an odd position##4
10. the person eating cauliflower is the fan of classical##1
11. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
12. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the social-worker##1
13. the person who's sport is handball is the person eating grapefruit##1
14. the fan of classical is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | cauliflower | pumpkin | lemon     | grapefruit |
| Job           | social-worker  | photographer   | scientist | analyst  |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | dubstep      | reggae     | rock   |
| Sport         | snowboarding | golf  | biathlon   | handball    |
| Transport     | van | jet-ski    | tram     | scooter |

