.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, hiking, magic-tricks, collecting
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, dressmaker, entrepreneur, engineer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, dubstep, indie, country
4 different pets are kept: mouse, turtle, ferret, chinchilla
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, skateboard, roller
 1. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 2. the fan of indie is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
 4. the fan of country is between the person driving the bike and the person driving the skateboard##2
 5. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 7. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
 8. the owner of the turtle is the person driving the car##1
 9. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
10. the dressmaker is on the left of the designer##1
11. the engineer is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is photography is the engineer##1
13. the engineer is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
14. the dressmaker is on the left or right of the designer##3
15. the entrepreneur is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |      3      |        4        |
| Hobby         | collecting | hiking    | photography | magic-tricks       |
| Job           | dressmaker | designer  | engineer   | entrepreneur |
| Music-Genre   | d&b   | dubstep     | country      | indie            |
| Pet           | mouse       | ferret      | turtle    | chinchilla           |
| Transport     | roller      | skateboard | car   | bike         |

