4 different pets are kept: pony, dog, rat, snake
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, rowing, sailing, golf
 1. the person who's sport is golf is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person eating corn##2
 2. the coach is in an even position##4
 3. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the coach##1
 4. the project-manager is in an even position##4
 5. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 6. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 7. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
 8. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
 9. the paramedic is the person eating pear##1
10. the person eating corn is the person watching zombie movies##1
11. the paramedic is the person watching drama movies##1
12. the owner of the rat is the person watching mystery movies##1
13. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4
14. the person eating corn is the project-manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |      3      |       4        |
