The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, baking, hiking, fishing
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, project-manager, engineer, dancer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, disaster, horror, crime
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 2. the person eating cabbage is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 4. the dancer is in an odd position##4
 5. the person watching fantasy movies is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 6. the writer is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person watching crime movies is the person who's hobby is reading##1
 8. the project-manager is the person drinking fanta##1
 9. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating avocado is the person drinking almond-milk##1
11. the person watching crime movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person eating corn is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
13. the person eating corn is in an odd position##4
14. the project-manager is between the person eating avocado and the person who's hobby is fishing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage      | cola    | almond-milk        | fanta      | soy-milk   |
