.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, almond-milk, juice, cola
There 4 different types of food: tomato, lemon, pomegranate, peas
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, fishing, filmmaking, card-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, action, disaster, sports
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, parkour, biathlon, rugby
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 3. the person who's sport is parkour is the person watching action movies##1
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person drinking juice##1
 5. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
 7. the person drinking cola is between the person watching disaster movies and the person watching sports movies##2
 8. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 9. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
10. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
11. the person eating lemon is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
12. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |      3       |    4     |
| Beverage      | juice    | cola      | almond-milk      | iced-tea |
| Food          | tomato | pomegranate | peas       | lemon |
| Hobby         | singing   | card-games   | fishing | filmmaking  |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster    | action    | sports      | satire   |
| Sport         | ice-hockey   | parkour     | biathlon       | rugby  |

