 3. the person driving the ship is in an even position##4
 4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 5. the person driving the bus is on the left of the dutch##1
 6. the person driving the bus is the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the person watching adventure movies is in an even position##4
