 9. the person who's sport is golf is the person driving the helicopter##1
10. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
12. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
13. the egyptian is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
14. the malaysian is in an odd position##4

