 4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
 6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 8. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
10. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person eating apricot##3
11. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
12. the person driving the van is in an odd position##4
13. the person watching disaster movies is the person eating artichoke##1
14. the person eating artichoke is the person drinking sprite##1
15. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3

