.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, magic-tricks, sudoku, skydiving
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, architect, coach, freelancer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, gospel, funk, metal
4 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, goat, frog
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, train, airplane, trike
 1. the person driving the bus is the owner of the dog##1
 2. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 3. the freelancer is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 6. the coach is on the left of the architect##1
 7. the owner of the hamster is the freelancer##1
 8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the owner of the dog##1
 9. the person driving the airplane is between the fan of funk and the architect##2
10. the person driving the train is on the far right##1
11. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left##1
12. the person driving the bus is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
13. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the architect##3
14. the architect is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | cooking       | magic-tricks    | skydiving | sudoku     |
| Job           | freelancer | coach  | architect  | photographer       |
| Music-Genre   | funk         | punk        | metal     | gospel |
| Pet           | hamster    | goat   | dog       | frog     |
| Transport     | trike          | airplane | bus      | train |

