.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, milk, tea, water
There 4 different types of food: plum, peach, blueberry, pepper
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, fisherman, coach, mechanic
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, scientific, drama, superhero
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, airplane, tram, van
 1. the person watching drama movies is in an odd position##4
 2. the mechanic is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 3. the doctor is the person drinking milk##1
 4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 5. the person driving the van is between the person drinking water and the fisherman##2
 6. the person driving the tram is on the far left##1
 7. the person drinking water is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 8. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3
 9. the fisherman is the person eating pepper##1
10. the person watching scientific movies is the person eating blueberry##1
11. the mechanic is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
12. the person watching musical movies is between the person driving the tram and the person watching scientific movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |     3      |       4       |
| Beverage      | sprite          | water     | milk       | tea |
| Food          | peach    | plum      | blueberry   | pepper          |
| Job           | coach   | mechanic | doctor   | fisherman   |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | musical    | scientific     | superhero        |
| Transport     | tram         | airplane    | van | snowmobile           |

