 4. the person driving the helicopter is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
 7. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
 8. the dutch is in an odd position##4
 9. the person driving the boat is on the right of the fan of country##1
10. the canadian is on the left or right of the dutch##3
11. the person who's sport is baseball is the brazilian##1
12. the fan of d&b is on the far left or far right##3
13. the fan of folk is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person who's sport is cycling##2
14. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the fan of folk##1
15. the fan of country is on the far left or far right##3

