The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, epic, action, western
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, trike, car, van
 1. the person driving the car is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 3. the person driving the trike is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 4. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 5. the person driving the van is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 7. the person watching action movies is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 8. the person eating plum is on the far left##1
 9. the person watching epic movies is in an odd position##4
10. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
11. the person driving the taxi is between the person watching epic movies and the person watching action movies##2
12. the person eating strawberry is the person drinking mirinda##1
13. the person driving the trike is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3     |       4       |
